issue.title: Playback
issue.body:
Server tries playing all songs added to the queue immediately after being added.
Plays the first song fine, but when a second song is added to the queue, the server plays it immediately, on top of the song that's already playing. 
The server is currently using the pyglet music player to play and queue up songs.

issue.title: Visualization
issue.body: Align all clients to see the song that is currently playing on the server, not the song that they just added to the queue.
